 19→ * - Adds 'globalMetrics' to the context (list of globally available metric infos)
 20→ * - Adds 'getMetricConfig' to the context, a function that takes a cluster, subCluster and metric name and returns the MetricConfig (or undefined)
 21→ * - Adds 'getHardwareTopology' to the context, a function that takes a cluster nad subCluster and returns the subCluster topology (or undefined)
